'''世界骨质疏松日'''（World Osteoporosis Day）是一个于1996年6月24日由英国国家骨质疏松学会创办纪念日。1998年，[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]将世界骨质疏松日改定为每年10月20日。由{{link-en|国际骨质疏松症基金会|International Osteoporosis Foundation}}（IOF）组织全球90多个国家开展活动，旨在提高预防，诊断和治疗[[骨质疏松症|骨质疏松症]]和[[代谢性骨病|代谢性骨病]]的认识。<ref name=ABC>{{cite web|url= http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2006/10/20/1769345.htm|title= IOF Releases Report for World Osteoporosis Day|year= 2011|accessdate= 2011-05-17|archive-date= 2011-02-16|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110216020330/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2006/10/20/1769345.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.zimbio.com/Osteoporosis/articles/_MfvYPXhwVB/World+Osteoporosis+Day+2010|title= World Osteoporosis Day Global Activities|year= 2011|accessdate= 2011-05-17|archive-date= 2012-10-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121014202732/http://www.zimbio.com/Osteoporosis/articles/_MfvYPXhwVB/World+Osteoporosis+Day+2010|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://ncdalliance.org/news-events/news/world-osteoporosis-day-theme-2016-announced |title=World Osteoporosis Day 2016 theme announced |year=2016 |accessdate=2020-04-05 |archive-date=2020-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604034610/https://ncdalliance.org/news-events/news/world-osteoporosis-day-theme-2016-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>

